tests.name: stack
tests.run: /usr/bin/timeout -k 1s -s 9 1s valgrind -q --leak-check=full --log-file=out.log ./a.out && if [[ `cat out.log | wc -l` -gt 0 ]]; then echo Memory leak detected; exit -1; fi

tests.name: queue
tests.setup: echo  | base64 -d > main.c && gcc main.c queue.c -lm
tests.run: /usr/bin/timeout -k 1s -s 9 1s valgrind -q --leak-check=full --log-file=out.log ./a.out && if [[ `cat out.log | wc -l` -gt 0 ]]; then echo Memory leak detected; exit -1; fi
